description:
Small sample of data for BioNLP Shared Task 2011 Main Task - Epigenetics and Post-translational Modifications (EPI)

- Contains 20 PubMed abstracts and their annotations.

- For format details, please refer to the shared task homepage.
  http://sites.google.com/site/bionlpst/

History:

 1 Dec 2010: initial version released.

14 Jan 2011: first revision released: 
   - manual revision of triggers (especially for Catalysis), "GPI anchor
     attachment" events, and a small number of errors in annotation.
   - automatic revision of references to entities with Equivs.
   - Equivs for non-Protein entities included.

Authors:

BioNLP Shared Task 2011 organizers,
bionlp-st@googlegroups.com
http://sites.google.com/site/bionlpst/
